</span></div><p itemprop="description">虽然都是樱桃红轴，但每个厂商的调教还是会有点不一样的，对比我原来用的G610，手感没那么软，下面是开箱图片。</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ammkqm6v/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a106533e3a8298.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="包装很大气"/></a>包装很大气</span></p><p itemprop="description" class="image-show-desc">包装很大气</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ammkqm6v/pic_3/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/05/5f2a1063e34b6422.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="背面介绍很详细"/></a>背面介绍很详细</span></p><p itemprop="description" class="image-show-desc">背面介绍很详细</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ammkqm6v/pic_4/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a106a4fe2b22.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="做工很好"/></a>做工很好</span></p><p itemprop="description" class="image-show-desc">做工很好</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ammkqm6v/pic_5/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/05/5f2a10724ede56706.jpg-180_e680.jpg" title="" alt="完美RGB"/></a>完美RGB</span></p><p itemprop="description" class="image-show-desc">完美RGB</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ammkqm6v/pic_6/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a10cf8b6b62886.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="灯效对比G610，颜值就是正义啊"/></a>灯效对比G610，颜值就是正义啊</span></p><p itemprop="description" class="image-show-desc">灯效对比G610，颜值就是正义啊</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ammkqm6v/pic_7/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a10704876b9288.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="侧面还有灯带"/></a>侧面还有灯带</span></p><p itemprop="description" class="image-show-desc">侧面还有灯带</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ammkqm6v/pic_8/' target='_