<p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description">最近更新了不少好看的<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/jiaojuwenju/" target="_blank">文具</a>，都是很简约的<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/shuxiegongju/" target="_blank">书写工具</a>。如果你也是简约派，那就一起来看看吧！</p><p itemprop="description" style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong>✒️  TWSBI Eco Cement Grey   </strong></span></p><p itemprop="description">近期Twsbi发布了ECO新色，水泥灰，预计在8月7日上市。</p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a259vgn7/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img alt="文具新草｜ Twsbi新色惹人爱，Kaweco限定款真够酷！" src="https://a.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a1f856270a149.jpg_e680.jpg" title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description">虽然钢尖会劝退不少“金尖党”，但也俘获了不少“颜值控”。不得不说这次更新的“性冷淡风”的配色，还挺高级的，很符合当下流行的“北欧风”设计。</p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a259vgn7/pic_3/' target='_blank'><img alt="文具新草｜ Twsbi新色惹人爱，Kaweco限定款真够酷！" src="https://a.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a1f856451a2458.jpg_e680.jpg" title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"> 所以当大家得知了新色的时候，纷纷表示“我可以！”。你可以吗？</p><p itemprop="description" style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong>✒️   Kaweco Black Crystal   </strong></span></p><p itemprop="description"> Black Crystal是kaweco Classic Sport系列中最新发布的限量配色，仅有1000支，并且只在北美地区独家发售。</p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a259vgn7/pic_4/' target='_blank'><img alt="文具新草｜ Twsbi新色惹人爱，Kaweco限定款真够酷！" src="https://a.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a1f856bf895392.jpg_e680.jpg" title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/gangbi/" target="_blank">钢笔</a>是带有黑色饰边的透明色钢笔，笔尖涂有黑色DLC涂层，据说是一种“类钻石涂层”，十分耐用。</p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://pos