同系列的轨迹灯，弧形线条细节有趣又不单调</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_47/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/05/5f2a19d4a3ac32982.png_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">二层是卧室，空间相对简单业主做了较为常规的配置，主卧架式床抛物线系列简约优美</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_48/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a19d4bdc545715.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_49/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a19d557b328535.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">搭配两个圆边<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/chuangtougui/" target="_blank">床头柜</a><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_50/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a19d559ea62915.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_51/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a19d55e5875328.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">黑胡桃木的的质感与纹路在灯光下更为凸显，与蓝色墙壁非常搭</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_52/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a19d630e5d6466.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">次卧选用经典架式床线条更硬朗<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_53/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a19d65175c277.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_54/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/