<p itemprop="description">上周杭州送货安装一个书柜，业主随手给我们拍了两张返图</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/05/5f2a194fa7fdc3709.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_3/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a1951917e45090.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">窗外满眼翠绿，屋内大书柜超级景观，在各平台掀起一波小轰动</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_4/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/05/5f2a19ccb12c26795.png_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">评论区快爆炸了，甚至，还有人打起了业主的主意，哈哈</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_5/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a19cd058d3218.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">这个订制为什么会有如此魔力呢？<br/></p><h2 id="cl_0">“装修从这面书柜开始说起”</h2><p itemprop="description">业主家是复式跃层</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_6/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a19ccd95b38501.png_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">建筑先天条件非常优越，客厅连接一个露台还有一大面落地窗</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_7/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a19cd03ecc1804.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_8/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a19cd02f032388.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">但户型有点老，厅比较深，旁边这面墙怎么安排业主一直没想好</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_9/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a19cd5247b7114.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">直到去年装修前，无意间看到良禽家业主飘飘订制的这面书墙👇</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_10/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a19cd9cca74239.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><strong>从颜色到材质，从功能到生活态度，正是想要的感觉。</strong>业主当即决定沟通订制。</p><p itemprop="description">先给这面墙一排书柜</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_11/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/05/5f2a19cdeb792914.png_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_12/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/05/5f2a19cdcf83c8214.png_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">再依托书柜来安排整体的家居搭配，这是一层俯视图</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_13/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/05/5f2a19cdf0f8a3602.png_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">来看看效果吧。</p><p itemprop="description">正对着客厅，这面书墙宛如一副大的沙发背景挂画</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_14/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a19ce3bd231548.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">黑胡桃木质地细腻，各个角度看都很简洁优雅</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_15/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a19ce74e7f9065.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7z3mnm/pic_16/' target='_blank'><img alt="200㎡露台复式，杭州业主靠这面书墙圈粉无数" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/05/5f2a19cea9b189978.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" 